<description><![CDATA[<h3>LogicGrid 10.1.3</h3>
<h4>Fixed</h4>
<ul>
<li>Detection strips no longer drift when Logic's "Show Global Tracks" is enabled. Previously, opening any global track row would cause the grid to mis-detect or fail to refine because Logic reports a taller ruler frame to Accessibility, which threw off our scan positions.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
